  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House", 
    "date": "2017-01-24T05:00:00Z", 
    "text": "Access to Inpatient Rehabilitation Therapy Act of 2017\n\nThis bill amends title XVIII (Medicare) of the Social Security Act to require the Centers for Medicare & Medicaid Services,\u00a0for purposes of\u00a0determining whether inpatient rehabilitation-facility services are reasonable and necessary under Medicare,\u00a0to include recreational-therapy services among the therapeutic modalities that constitute an intensive rehabilitation-therapy program."
